s/lny/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T13:03:40.000Z","msg":"因為第一局賺一蚊即走既機率係1/2，但其實仲有其他可能性。你可以先輸一局，再贏兩局，或者先輸兩局再贏三局，有好多好多可能性。所有可能性夾埋就係10/11。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T13:26:10.000Z","msg":"對唔住巴打 我柒咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a2909cef9df8725be726126e46498521a03a90e","tid":1012262,"uid":56097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b7b356dd99ad1c658447d36f95c7160fc255158","tid":1012262,"uid":61991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f4531084fef315af5950bb5779f499b2a5e940da","tid":1012262,"uid":56097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a95c497317d4cf9764b960205810189341b0894e","tid":1012262,"uid":61991,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T12:33:54.000Z","msg":"其實股票市場都係咁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T13:17:21.000Z","msg":"股票市場 賭期貨一樣可以好公平 每1點期貨 10/50蚊<br />\n手續費買連賣15蚊 都有貼近公平既產品既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T13:19:15.000Z","msg":"就係話即使係公平既產品，但仍然係散戶輸多，大行贏多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T13:27:02.000Z","msg":"敢輸唔敢贏 輸左搏翻身 贏就會諗割禾青 止賺止蝕訂唔清楚<br />\n自制能力 贏/輸完即刻再買返 驚贏唔切走寶<br />\n股票市場百分70%時間係唔適合入貨 致勝關鍵都係等<br />\n人唔係機器 有情感因素 唔訂規矩/目標落場會出事<br />\n諗住贏 但係贏幾多？ 唔通無盡咩？<br />\n同埋人地大公司大機構 團隊運作<br />\n散戶/獨立投資者只要有一次唔小心都會輸<br />\n同埋無可能100%贏 要接受自己會輸 同埋分散資金 孤注一擲 輸左就破產 我就波馬股賭都縱橫十幾年 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8a56c25c0e7bef7c6407745f859c2c640c317c0","tid":1012262,"uid":215634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db3aa88ad455b4be781c9f945dae3487940655ce","tid":1012262,"uid":7438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"551966d43df6b26b6ceafc4caaa42e24cd4f566d","tid":1012262,"uid":215634,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"48c6497d48f175789f585d1aa0cd98758a871c50","tid":1012262,"uid":7438,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T12:54:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>計算可知賭徒成功達到目標b元離場嘅機率為a/b</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n哩個位唔太明，可能因為我頂唔順蝗話冇睇哂片<br />\n但考慮一個隨意嘅case，我本金有$10，升到$11就走，理應我有1/2機會達到目標，但代落a/b條式度得出10/11<br />\n<br />\n唔make sense咁喎ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T13:03:40.000Z","msg":"因為第一局賺一蚊即走既機率係1/2，但其實仲有其他可能性。你可以先輸一局，再贏兩局，或者先輸兩局再贏三局，有好多好多可能性。所有可能性夾埋就係10/11。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T13:26:10.000Z","msg":"對唔住巴打 我柒咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T13:40:03.000Z","msg":"有唔明歡迎發問<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大家學野"},{"pid":"1dffdd462d957f097e3948d14e9a8d5ffa10667d","tid":1012262,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c6bd4befd08d4579be7cc25144f566c4f47cfde","tid":1012262,"uid":85116,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T12:33:09.000Z","msg":"其實依啲你知我知大家都知,但係爛賭鬼係非理性的<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T16:18:43.000Z","msg":"咁又唔係，我第一次睇到，<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6e3fd2a804013f2dc665b59a0262c890eb0768f","tid":1012262,"uid":233026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T16:20:17.000Z","msg":"你係咪賭sir d朋友<br />\n定係你係賭sir<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"227c1d0db4c12a3b0d330b9eead298f198ec8309","tid":1012262,"uid":135445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T16:21:20.000Z","msg":"賭場既game set好哂<br />\n所有game既EV一定細過0(winning prob細過1/2)<br />\n根據law of large number<br />\n你玩得越多場<br />\n長久黎講一定會係蝕"},{"pid":"09e889398d82cce027f037f702eb5d8fedb9d393","tid":1012262,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"c8a56c25c0e7bef7c6407745f859c2c640c317c0","